                            ★★★★★
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" class="rounded-circle me-3" alt="Client 2">
                            <div>
                                <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Jane Smith</h5>
                                <small class="text-muted">Marketing Director</small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="card-text">"The results we've achieved together have exceeded our expectations. Their innovative approach and dedication are truly remarkable."</p>
                        <div class="text-warning">
                            ★★★★★
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50" class="rounded-circle me-3" alt="Client 3">
                            <div>
                                <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Mike Johnson</h5>
                                <small class="text-muted">Startup Founder</small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="card-text">"Their expertise and professionalism have been instrumental in our success. I couldn't recommend them more highly."</p>
                        <div class="text-warning">
                            ★★★★★
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Testimonials Section -->

    <!-- All other homepage sections restored below (about, services, portfolio, blog, contact, etc.) -->
    <!-- Please copy the rest of your index.html content here, updating all image paths to start with /images/ -->

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
            if (window.scrollY > 50) {
                document.querySelector('.navbar').classList.add('scrolled');
            } else {
                document.querySelector('.navbar').classList.remove('scrolled');
            }
        });
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
